{"tid":2339012,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"越南宣布對中國部分鋼鐵產品 加課4.43%-25.22%反傾銷稅","createTime":"2020-12-24T10:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T00:02:01.000Z","uid":362199,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a04a8529f6bb780b6d2efb3ea3cbe31b6edb6d7d","tid":2339012,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4553894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4553894&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtwg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=39a4ef64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4553894</a><br />\n<br />\n越南工業和貿易部周三 (23 日) 表示，從 12 月 28 日起，越南將對自中國 16 家鋼鐵生產商進口的一些冷軋鋼材產品，徵收 4.43%-25.22% 的反傾銷關稅，為期 5 年。<br />\n<br />\n工貿部指出，根據自去年 9 月開始的反傾銷調查，認為由中國進口的傾銷鋼材，可能對越南的鋼鐵業造成重大損害。在調查期間由中國進口的冷軋鋼達到 27.2 萬噸，占越南進口的冷軋鋼總量的 65.5%。<br />\n<br />\n調查認為，由利潤、庫存和市場份額等關鍵指標顯示，它對越南國內製造業帶來了巨大的損害威脅。<br />\n<br />\n此前，越南一直表示，正在打擊中國商品透過「洗產地」方式，標記為越南製產品銷往美國。"},{"pid":"8c0410363c34a0e08e3cc181223a22518f9c5eeb","tid":2339012,"uid":186915,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"石頭 腳"},{"pid":"f95f516eaf5800939a876f4dbcd3cb1c71f61d4e","tid":2339012,"uid":243677,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"越南<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b22b52b2620ebb686c89cce23e1b3157e2dd70","tid":2339012,"uid":321002,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:49:27.000Z","msg":"剃人頭者，人亦剃其頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f8b94c333fa3fd126c002569ea0f93d43adcde","tid":2339012,"uid":40267,"like":4,"disli